info.author: Frank T. Bergmann
info.description: libNuML is a library for reading, writing and manipulating NuML.  It is written in ISO C and C++, supports NuML Level 1, Version 1, and runs on Linux, Microsoft Windows, and Apple MacOS X.  For more information about SEDML, please see http://github.com/numl/numl/.
info.name: python-libnuml
